Ariana Village - Amenities and Activities
Ariana Village - Amenities and Activities
Relaxing 55+ Living in Lakeland, Florida
Ariana Village is a charming 55+ community in Lakeland, Florida, with a welcoming, small-town feel. Enjoy an array of amenities and activities as you make new friends and take up new hobbies. Get together on the garden patio and relax in the heated outdoor pool and spa. Enjoy some play time on our shuffleboard courts or horseshoe pits. Meet for social events and classes in the clubhouse, play a a game in the billiards room, or grab a book from the library. Our courteous management staff are ready to provide the highest level of customer service.
Clubhouse
Meet in our community clubhouse to socialize and relax with friends. Enjoy planned activities, arts and craft workshops, a library, billards, and card tables. Residents can also host special events in our banquet space with a kitchen.
Swimming Pool
Take a refreshing dip in our heated swimming pool. Our outdoor pool is the perfect place to relax and soak up the sunshine.
Fitness Room
Stay active and healthy in our fitness room, featuring state-of-the-art equipment. Hit your fitness goals, stay in shape, and feel your best.
Dog Park
Bring the pups to our community dog park for off-leash fun and exercise. Our well-maintained dog park is perfect for dogs and their owners to enjoy the outdoors.
Gated Community
Our gated community offers peace of mind and security for all residents with controlled access. Enjoy the added privacy and exclusivity of living in a gated community.
All Amenities
Stay active, relaxed and entertained at our beautiful Florida community. Whether you want to play, socialize or take up a new sport, Ariana Village offer the vibrant lifestyle you deserve.

Ariana Village
Relaxing 55+ Living in Lakeland, Florida!
Tucked away in the heart of charming Lakeland, Ariana Village is a beautiful 55+ community nestled in Central Florida. Experience a small-town neighborhood feel in a lush setting with acres of trees and foliage that remove you from the bustle of downtown. We are conveniently located close to shopping, entertainment, dining, and attractions, including Polk Museum of Art, Bok Tower Gardens, and Lake Morton to name just a few.
Our lovely garden community offers resort-style amenities and activities, including a clubhouse, heated swimming pool, and relaxing hot tub. Get energized in the fitness center or meet new friends over shuffleboard. Other amenities include billiards and horseshoe pits. Live the active 55+ life you've always dreamed of, in beautiful Ariana Village.

Discover
Just east of Tampa, in the heart of charming Lakeland, Florida, we are minutes from downtown, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Visit the Colt Street State Park and the Munn Park Historic District. Grab a friend and see nearby attractions such as Safari Wilderness and the Florida Air Museum. Take advantage of easy access to Tampa Bay and the Gulf of Mexico.

Bok Tower Gardens
Lake Morton

Is Lakeland, Florida, a good place to live?
Is Lakeland, Florida, a good place to live?
Nestled in central Florida, Lakeland is a fantastic place to call home. Enjoy the convenience of being close to larger cities such as Tampa and Orlando, offering endless opportunities for entertainment and adventure. Lakeland is renowned for its diverse Florida wildlife, and abundant waterways have earned it the nickname Swan City.
How much is a new manufactured home in Lakeland, Florida?
How much is a new manufactured home in Lakeland, Florida?
The cost of our quality-built manufactured homes varies. We offer many
affordable homes
with access to complimentary community amenities for even more value. Please contact our team for pricing and more information
What recreational activities are offered at Ariana Village?
What recreational activities are offered at Ariana Village?
In addition to our clubhouse with heated swimming pool and large hot tub, fitness center, billiards, and library, we have an extensive woodworking shop, craft clubs, and dances. Enjoy fantastic
amenities
in the place you call home.
What are the best attractions in Lakeland, Florida?
What are the best attractions in Lakeland, Florida?
The Frances Langford Promenade, Lake Mirror, and the Lakeland Downtown Farmer's Market are well-known spots to enjoy in Lakeland. Enjoy a movie at the historic Polk Theatre. Discover unique places to eat and drink as well as enjoy live entertainment, downtown shopping, and local artisans and markets.
